responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "3F3E23014D2D97CA57D519869FAA3152", "Under the moons veil we found ourselves upon the main horde of the Priestess. We were outnumbered and had no hope of victory there, yet our goal was not that. We  retreated to the Citadel and set our snare for the demoness. She followed as we expected, no doubt expecting to smite our gods by extinguishing our flame of rightousness.")
